          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector array consisted of",
                "two twin, large area, position sensitive telescopes.",
                "Each telescope involved two silicon strip detectors",
                "for dE and position measurements and one CsJ crystal",
                "for energy measurements."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SOLST",
                "SOLST"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The 8He beam was monitored and its",
                "intensity measured using a system of two plastic",
                "scintillators. A thin, 200 mu-m plastic was set before",
                "the target, whereas a thick plastic scintillator",
                "serving as a beam stopper was installed behind the",
                "target."
              ]
            }
          ],
